# Real-Time Cryptocurrency Trading Analytics Pipeline

[![Build Status](https://github.com/your-repo/crypto-pipeline/workflows/CI/badge.svg)](https://github.com/your-repo/crypto-pipeline/actions)
[![Coverage Status](https://codecov.io/gh/your-repo/crypto-pipeline/branch/main/graph/badge.svg)](https://codecov.io/gh/your-repo/crypto-pipeline)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

## Overview

A comprehensive, production-ready data engineering pipeline that processes real-time cryptocurrency trading data using modern big data technologies. This project demonstrates enterprise-level data engineering practices with AWS cloud services, Apache Spark, and real-time streaming analytics.

## Architecture

![Architecture Diagram](docs/architecture-diagram.png)

### Key Components:
- **Data Ingestion**: AWS Lambda + Kinesis Data Streams
- **Stream Processing**: Apache Spark Structured Streaming on EMR
- **Data Storage**: S3 Data Lake + DynamoDB
- **Analytics**: AWS Glue + Amazon Athena
- **Orchestration**: Apache Airflow (MWAA)
- **Monitoring**: CloudWatch + Grafana
- **Infrastructure**: Terraform (IaC)

## Technologies Used

### Big Data & Processing
- **Apache Spark 3.4+** - Distributed computing and stream processing
- **PySpark** - Python API for Spark applications
- **Spark Structured Streaming** - Real-time data processing
- **Apache Airflow** - Workflow orchestration

### Cloud Services (AWS)
- **Amazon Kinesis** - Real-time data streaming
- **AWS EMR** - Managed Spark clusters
- **Amazon S3** - Data lake storage
- **Amazon DynamoDB** - NoSQL database for real-time data
- **AWS Glue** - Data catalog and ETL
- **Amazon Athena** - Serverless SQL analytics
- **AWS Lambda** - Serverless data ingestion
- **Amazon MWAA** - Managed Apache Airflow

### DevOps & Infrastructure
- **Terraform** - Infrastructure as Code
- **Docker** - Containerization
- **GitHub Actions** - CI/CD pipeline
- **CloudWatch** - Monitoring and logging

### Data Sources
- **Binance API** - Cryptocurrency price data
- **CoinGecko API** - Market data and metrics

## Features

### Real-Time Analytics
- Live cryptocurrency price monitoring
- Technical indicators (RSI, MACD, Moving Averages)
- Anomaly detection using statistical methods
- Market volatility analysis
- Cross-asset correlation analysis

### Data Engineering Best Practices
- **Lambda Architecture** - Batch and stream processing layers
- **Schema Evolution** - Handle API changes gracefully
- **Data Quality Checks** - Automated validation and monitoring
- **Exactly-Once Processing** - Idempotent data processing
- **Auto-scaling** - EMR clusters scale with data volume

### Production Features
- **High Availability** - Multi-AZ deployment
- **Disaster Recovery** - Automated backups and recovery
- **Security** - IAM roles, VPC, encryption at rest/transit
- **Cost Optimization** - Spot instances, lifecycle policies
- **Monitoring & Alerting** - Custom metrics and dashboards